Subject: [PATCH] fix: restore old vibe kanban experience

Disables cloud migration prompts to preserve the original local-first
experience which is better suited for agent orchestration workflows.

Changes:
- Redirect root URL (/) to /local-projects instead of cloud UI
- Disable BetaWorkspacesDialog modal that prompts migration on page load
- Hide migration alert box on kanban dashboard
- Remove unused imports and variables (Cloud, ExternalLink, Sparkles, BetaWorkspacesDialog)

These changes are applied as a downstream patch to maintain the
preferred local project workflow.
